Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:43.54,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(824,605)}{\blur3}第８話「妹妹‧突擊！」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹老是問我 真醬最近怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真醬是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,部長 別把巧克力沾到書上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,過一會我和Tama還要看的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 這是Pocky啊 怎樣才會沾到書上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 怎麼會沾到書上呢 不可思議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 真醬是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是部長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,飛得好遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼慌張幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,至今為止 沒人給真央起過可愛的愛稱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因為大家都害怕她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要求重取！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼真…真…真醬啊 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,愛稱不都是傻傻的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的Kyoron聽起來也相當傻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,取名的不就是部長你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,亂說 取名的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是惠 我是被冤枉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoron 是吧 很配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是真醬算什麼啊…完全不適合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊 因為霞以為部長比她小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊去給我消除誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是部長你自己隱藏的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,說暴露高中生身份很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因為 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你…那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事那麼害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 真央 你什麼時候見過Kyoron的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 呃 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那是和部長兩個人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那件事不要爆出來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是因為難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因為想吃兒童套餐而假扮你的妹妹什麼的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,假扮妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是這麼想的 真央希望自己能成為妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,根據弗洛伊德的理論…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 原來如此 部長是長女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,生下來一直都是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我有時候也羨慕別人的弟弟 我能明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也一直是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但聖羅出生後我也就成了姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama是獨生女吧 這麼任性的人肯定是獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama不是獨生女Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有弟弟啊妹妹呀弟弟啊妹妹呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不能獨占零食Death嘎嘎～的吵死人了Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以Tama變成了這麼文靜的女生Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,後半的台詞就無視掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,綺羅羅 也有 妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,叫小傑拉丁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,傑拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,叫小傑拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 愛稱一般都省略的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 部長叫真醬就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼疼 疼 部長 真的很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼今天咬得那麼狠啊！疼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 今天霞要來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說過 小霞問我真醬最近怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不許叫真醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天回家跟霞說 被真醬咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,於是 她問我在哪裡咬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我就說是在社辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在編不出真醬的其他謊了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,說了不許叫真醬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 這是GJ部的活動室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 這裡是活動室Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama…你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,霞 我不是說過 到學校就打電話給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因為要捉姦在床啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因為哥哥可能在做H的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有做啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 指路的人勸我不要靠近這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 哥哥一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,作為妹妹 要先好好打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 我是四之宮霞 今年開始讀中學一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥承蒙各位的照顧了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoron的 妹妹的 味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 咦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真狡猾 我也可以抱抱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,口渴了嗎 還有蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹什麼的一點都不可愛Death煩人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…這些人都是GJ部的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真醬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真醬也來這裡玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞 哎嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,部長！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真醬真的在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說要消除誤會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事情要講究時機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真央是惠姐姐的妹妹nano～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道的設定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真央 妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 難怪能經常跟哥哥見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 或許經常見面 幾乎每天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但為什麼叫部長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥叫真醬部長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼叫部長？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我有說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,切！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HAC&}綽號 說是綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對對 那是綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真醬跟公司社長一樣 整天指手畫腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是小學生為什麼來高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HAC&}作業 說來做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對對 做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來這裡要我們教她做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊勒 感覺真醬的作業好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那隻豬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,最近小學三年級的作業怎麼那麼難 數學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:53.21,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\move(498,185,498,-81,32,4954)\c&H000000&}決定數列各項的公式 稱作遞進公式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:53.21,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\move(542,425,542,144,32,4954)\c&H000000&}求出下列數列的一般項
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是私立小學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.89,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：日本私立學校為了追求升學率 課時比公立學校長 學習內容比公立學校深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,接受了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好難啊 我會做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 真醬 我可以做做看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 關鍵部分還不明白Death
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,部長和學長為什麼要去家庭餐廳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,細節就別追究啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 真央不想讓別人知道自己是高中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就盡力幫助你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,軟妹模式的真央感覺相當不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 部長 你剛剛露出真面目囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 裝嫩好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,部長的真醬模式 比我的俺曼模式續航時間還短呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,切 還不如Kyoron啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,做出來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,V！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害啊 霞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡數學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,部長能解答那道題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼 疼啊 真的很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.68,Comment,,0,0,0,,為什麼咬我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,出現了 小真央的咬人絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我咬！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再用力點 再激烈點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,懷著「你這個混蛋」的心情 融入怒火！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真醬是這麼覺得的喲～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 疼疼 疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙 不妙 不妙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯了 放過我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,疼 霞 好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,開電風扇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,省電
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,電風扇也用不了多少電
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想這是社團活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,「我想」是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這是社團活動嗎 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是社團活動的話 就別忍了涼快涼快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,學長姐 吵死了Death喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,越吵越熱 閉嘴Death喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,別發牢騷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,氣勢 要有氣勢啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,滅卻心頭夏自涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:23.47,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：原句為「滅卻心頭火自涼」快川紹喜被燒死時的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看紫 學著點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼熱的天氣下仍一如往常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,冷血體質嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,綺羅羅～還活著嗎～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小惠 怎麼樣了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 忍不住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,給我扇！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 要互相扇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 應該當然啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真的真的真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等會要公平公正地換班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該換班了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不肯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界上有兩種人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,扇風的人和吹風的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不肯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,別哭啦 給你獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 明天大家一起去游泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你們在鬧哪樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼穿著泳裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,去游泳池 當然要穿泳裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個 為什麼現在就穿上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,穿普通衣服會濕掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快點去游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人還沒到齊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 是真醬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 小霞～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真醬已經換好泳裝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因為等不及了嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還叫了霞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 今天要拜託你當監護人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友也會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,責任重大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不會游泳也沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小傑拉也放心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小傑拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 外國女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,藍藍的眼睛 金色的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很可愛啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,像芭比娃娃一樣～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,小傑拉 在哪裡聽過…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還有聖羅親也要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我說聖羅親我也不認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,部長 部長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Y…You！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 這孩子在哪見過…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Do you remember me？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你還記得我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}I I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,霞 求翻譯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用翻譯的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小傑拉日語很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Hey Jill, you must use your whiteboard
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,傑拉 你要用你的白板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Oh my god
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,偶買高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}My mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,您還記得我嗎 我的絕地武士！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,絕地武士？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被你幫助的那個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是幫助了我的那位武士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,幫助了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～那時候的女孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟小傑拉是朋友啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 以前見過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候 見過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上二年級之前 只見過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,二年級之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 傑拉一直說的出色的日本男子就是哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(748,650)}楠幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 出色的日本男子什麼的 自己都覺得有違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你幫助了小傑拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼大不了的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只是教她怎麼買票而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoron 武士？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Sister！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Xisuta？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,綺羅羅的妹妹啦 她不是叫傑拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,傑拉 you are 霞's friend？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Yes！unbelievable！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真是巧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Why are you here？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}How do you know samurai？sisiter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐是怎麼認識武士的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 巧合還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 聖羅親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是聖羅你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦姐姐大人～霞說要介紹真醬給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 我是真央～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都叫我真醬～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,別廢話 配合老娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你腦袋很好 應該知道狀況了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是天使家的次女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,惠姐姐是長女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然後小真央是三女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,設定成小學三年級 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,完美！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,部長 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,把你那骯髒的手從姐姐身上挪開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就趕快立即馬上去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,四之宮京夜大人是霞的哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,霞一直都把我當成是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好 全員到齊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoron 你可以退場了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來我們要準備準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,男生退場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 咦～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真醬她們是泳裝 我們也換了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不是穿衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮地東張西望了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是Kyoron
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因為沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了未經允許別讓我們家的女僕轉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是我讓她轉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 快滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,換衣服了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,咦～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:20:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,游泳之後直接去逛廟會是常識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是常識啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,噗噗噗 又歡快地東張西望了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個混蛋 怎麼老是讓別人家的女僕轉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了不是我讓她轉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoron你作為紳士 應該稍加節制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,森小姐和四之宮同學關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦 哥哥 那樣會變成男生的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Master？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,極度鄙視這大便！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoron 轉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣Death學長也來轉Death吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
